  "texts": [
    "These centers act as one-stop shops where citizens can access a wide range of public services, including legal documentation and case information, through digital platforms. i.",
    "Key Interventions: Kenya: Huduma Centers and Digitized Legal Services• Centralized Service Access.",
    "Huduma Centers provide citizens with access to legal services such as marriage registration, business name searches, and land ownership verification through a digitized system.",
    "• Mobile and Web Platforms.",
    "The Kenyan government has introduced mobile platforms that allow citizens to apply for legal documents and services from their phones."
  ]
